spec_data.Name: texlive-pxpgfmark
spec_data.Description:
The distributed drivers do not support the PGF feature of
"inter-picture connections" under e-pTeX and dvipdfmx. The
package uses existing features of dvipdfmx to fix this problem
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 08:01:35 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: e-pTeX driver for PGF inter-picture connections
